\b  
\li1
\v 5 The tribe of Issachar will camp next to it. The leader of the Issacharites is Nethanel son of Zuar,  
\v 6 and his division numbers 54,400.   
\b  
\li1
\v 7 Next will be the tribe of Zebulun. The leader of the Zebulunites is Eliab son of Helon,  
\v 8 and his division numbers 57,400.   
\b  
\pmo
\v 9 \w The|strong="H3605"\w* \w total|strong="H3605"\w* \w number|strong="H6485"\w* \w of|strong="H6635"\w* \w men|strong="H3605"\w* \w in|strong="H6635"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* divisions \w of|strong="H6635"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w camp|strong="H4264"\w* \w of|strong="H6635"\w* \w Judah|strong="H3063"\w* \w is|strong="H3605"\w* 186,400; \w they|strong="H3605"\w* \w shall|strong="H3063"\w* \w set|strong="H5265"\w* \w out|strong="H5265"\w* \w first|strong="H7223"\w*.   
