\b  
\li1
\v 14 Next will be the tribe of Gad. The leader of the Gadites is Eliasaph son of Deuel,\f + \fr 2:14 \ft Many MT manuscripts, SP, and Vulgate (see also Numbers 1:14); most MT manuscripts Reuel\f*  
