\s1 Murmuring and Plague  
\r (1 Corinthians 10:1–13)  
\b  
\m
\v 41 The next day the whole congregation of Israel grumbled against Moses and Aaron, saying, “You have killed the \w LORD|strong="H3068"\w*’s people!”  
\v 42 But when the congregation gathered against them, Moses and Aaron turned toward the Tent of Meeting, and suddenly the cloud covered it and the glory of the \w LORD|strong="H3068"\w* appeared.   
\b  
